<meta name="assert" value="This test verifies that, given ::selection styles with both color and background-color declared as unset, both properties inherit their values from the parent ::selection styles. All properties become inherited for the purposes of deciding whether unset should mean initial or inherit."><main class="highlight_reftest">
</main><script src="support/selections.js"></script>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<style>
    main {
        font-size: 7em;
        margin: 0.5em;
    }
    main::selection {
        background-color: green;
        color: white;
    }
    main > span::selection {
        background-color: unset;
    }
</style>
<p>Test passes if the text below is white on green.
